altTitle: 毎日死ね死ね言ってくる義妹が、俺が寝ている隙に催眠術で惚れさせようとしてくるんですけど……!
My stepsister who says Go die go die to me every day, tries to hypnotize me to fall for her while I was sleeping...!
title: Mainichi Shine Shine Itte Kuru Gimai ga, Ore ga Neteiru Suki ni Saimin-jutsu de Hore Saseyou to Shite Kurundesu kedo…!
